videos.description: Dillon Stoner makes a great tip-toeing reception which sets up the Cowboys' Dezmon Jackson for the short rushing touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stoner's great grab sets up Jackson's TD for Oklahoma State) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stoner's great grab sets up Jackson's TD for Oklahoma State

videos.description: Jelani Woods jukes the defender to get the Cowboys closer to the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma State's Woods breaks ankles on 46-yard reception) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Woods breaks ankles on 46-yard reception

videos.description: Derius Davis hauls in a 31-yard catch with a defender on his back for the Horned Frogs' first down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (TCU's Davis makes 31-yard grab to set up TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: TCU's Davis makes 31-yard grab to set up TD

videos.description: Max Duggan keeps the ball for himself and breaks free for the 42-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (TCU's Duggan keeps it on the option and goes 42 yards for TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: TCU's Duggan keeps it on the option and goes 42 yards for TD

videos.description: Zach Evans powers his way into the end zone for the 1-yard touchdown giving the Horned Frogs their first lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Evans muscles in for TCU's go-ahead TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evans muscles in for TCU's go-ahead TD

videos.description: Spencer Sanders launches it 55 yards deep to a loosely covered Tylan Wallace, who scores the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma State's Sanders, Wallace connect for deep TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Sanders, Wallace connect for deep TD

videos.description: Max Duggan sails it deep down the field for Derius Davis, who caps off the big play with a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (TCU regains lead with Davis' 71-yard TD) 2020/12/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: TCU regains lead with Davis' 71-yard TD

videos.description: Spencer Sanders gets airborne as he tries to hurdle a TCU defender and ends up flipping head over heels for the first down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sanders flips over defender for the Oklahoma State first down) 2020/12/05 ESHEET
